text: The 2022 South Dakota gubernatorial election took place on November 8, 2022, electing the governor of South Dakota. Current Republican governor Kristi Noem beat Democratic nominee Jamie Smith to win a second term. ==References== Category:November 2022 events Category:Gubernatorial elections in the United States Category:2020s in South Dakota Category:2022 elections in the United States
title: 2022 South Dakota gubernatorial election
